- 'At least 5 feedback entries' ensures that the ratings are based on a sufficient number of customer opinions.

- "Top 5 most popular" refers to the sizes with the highest number of units sold;
- "Past month" refers to the last 30 days from the current date;
- "Average customer ratings" are calculated by averaging the ratings given by customers for each size.

